px; width: 555px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; position: absolute; top: 25px; margin: 0px; left: 35px;\" class=\"design-mode-hidden\"><label style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 320px; border-style: solid; text-rendering: optimizespeed; color: rgb(77, 87, 95); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-family: &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; padding: 2px 15px; height: 16px; position: absolute; left: 107px; top: 54px; width: 283px;\" id=\"url_chrome\" class=\"\">https://www.ticketmaster.com/taylor-swift</label><label style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 320px; border-style: solid; text-rendering: optimizespeed; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding: 2px 15px; width: 180px; height: 20px; position: absolute; left: 327px; top: 105px; text-align: right;\" id=\"visitor_count_label\" class=\"design-mode-hidden\">0</label></div><div class=\"screen\" tabindex=\"1\" data-theme=\"default\" id=\"screen2\" style=\"height: 450px; width: 600px; left: 0px; top: 0px; position: absolute; z-index: 0; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); display: none;\"><div contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"textArea\" id=\"text_area1\" style=\"width: 365px; height: 200px; border-style: solid; background-color: rgba(242, 242, 242, 0); color: rgb(113, 255, 0); border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); border-radius: 2px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 130px; top: 215px; margin: 0px; text-align: center;\">YOUR FILES ARE ENCRYPTED!!!<div><